data.description: Welcome to 1100 Balkan Drive! Conveniently located in the beautiful Whispering Pines neighborhood sits this meticulously maintained gem. The first floor consists of the den/home office, dining room, powder room, eat in kitchen and family room. The kitchen is open to the family room making the perfect space to entertain (or watch the kids!) while you cook. You will be amazed by the beautiful custom-built deck complete with an open gable roof complemented by a knotty pine ceiling, composite decking and vinyl railing. Enjoy the view from your deck while relaxing with your family! The second floor has your bedrooms which are all of generous size. The master bedroom is huge and is complete with a large walk-in closet and ensuite master bathroom. The back yard has a brand-new black aluminum fence perfect for the kids and pets. The game room is finished with ceramic tile flooring making the perfect man-cave or playroom!
